name: Neo-Cretaceous Britney
description:
NEO-CRETACEOUS BRITNEY

You're a popstar trapped in a tyrannosaur body, the patriarchy weren't ready for you though, and made you go to rehab due to your addiction to the flesh of your enemies. Stick it to da'man the only way you can, violently.

(Chrome will have problems playing this format)

A university project, let me know your thoughts, I'm making a new one that is hopefully going to be a lot better though similar.
